# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Notes:
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. This .gitignore is optimized for Python + Pygame projects
# 2. It follows GitHub's official gitignore templates:
#    - Python.gitignore
#    - Global/macOS.gitignore
#    - Global/Windows.gitignore
#    - Global/Linux.gitignore
# 3. Environment variables (.env) are excluded to prevent
#    accidental commit of API keys and secrets
# 4. Game data files are excluded to protect user privacy
# 5. All rules are tested to avoid excluding necessary files
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
airwar/airwar/data/user_docking_save.json
airwar/airwar/data/users.json
